  <summary date="2020-04-16T19:30:24Z" status="Introduced in House">Educational Freedom Accounts Act

This bill (1) establishes an educational savings account program for District of Columbia children who are eligible to receive a free public education in the District, but whose parents choose not to enroll them in a public school or home schooling; and (2) specifies the use of such funds, including for private schools.</summary>
